cards.rules_text:
When Sealing Blade enters, exile up to one target nonland permanent until this artifact leaves the battlefield.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1.
Equip {2}

When Vakhter's Edge enters, you may attach it to target creature you control. When you do, target creature can't block this turn.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and has haste.
Equip {3}

When Sunward Spear enters, create a Hunt battle token an opponent protects with 2 defense and “When this battle is defeated, create a 4/4 white Angel creature token with flying.”
Equipped creature gets +2+0 and has flying.
Equip {2}

When Horizon's Edge enters, mill four cards. You may return a creature or land card milled this way to your hand.
Equipped creature gets +X/+X, where X is the number of creature and/or land cards in your graveyard.
Equip {5}

When Pendant of Good Harvests enters, you may search your library for a basic land card, reveal it, put it into your hand, then shuffle.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has “Whenever this creature attacks, scry 1.”
Equip {1}

When Stiltwalker Husk enters, create a 1/1 green Human creature token, then attach Stiltwalker Husk to it.
Equipped creature gets +4/+4 and has reach.
Equip {6}

Equipped creature has double strike.
If equipped creature attacking causes a triggered ability of a permanent you control to trigger, that ability triggers an additional time.
Equip {2}

{T}: Add {C}. If Tiller of Realms is equipped to a creature, add {C}{C} instead.
Equipped creature gets +3/+3.
Equip {5}

When Garland of Trez enters, create three 2/2 green Wolf creature tokens. They gain haste until end of turn.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, creatures you control get +2/+0 until end of turn.
Equip {4}

When Fateful Beacon enters, if you cast it, you may search your library for a creature card with mana value 2 or less, put it onto the battlefield, attach Fateful Beacon to it, then shuffle.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and has vigilance.
Equip {3}

When The Thirsting Pane enters, attach The Thirsting Pane to target creature you don't control and gain control of it for as long as The Thirsting Pane is attached to it. Tap that creature and put three stun counters on it.
Equipped creature gets +2/+1 and has “Whenever this creature attacks, draw a card.”
Equip {3}

When Woundlace Doll enters, create a 2/2 red Human creature token, then attach Woundlace Doll to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1 and has wither. [i](This deals damage to creatures in the form of -1/-1 counters.)[/i]
Equip {3}

Equipped creature gets +1/+0 for each charge counter on Lifebinder's Bough.
Whenever you gain life, put a charge counter on Lifebinder's Bough. If Lifebinder's Bough isn't equipped to a creature, you may equip it to a creature you control instead.
Equip {5}

