When Standard of the Risen Blade enters, return target creature card with mana value 3 or less from your graveyard to the battlefield, then attach Standard of the Risen Blade to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+1.
Equip {2}

When Confessor's Thorn enters, draw two cards, then discard a card.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has “Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player or noncreature permanent, you may return an Equipment attached to it to its owner's hand.”
Equip {2}

Equipped creature gets +1/-1.
Whenever equipped creature dies, you draw a card and you lose 1 life.
Equip {2}

Whenever Bundle of Borrowed Charms enters, create a 2/2 red Human creature token, then attach Bundle of Borrowed Charms to it.
Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has trample.
Equip {2}
